==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Puling
<hw>Pul"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A cry, as of a
chicken,; a whining or whimpering.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Leave this faint <qex>puling</qex> and lament as I do.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Puling</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Puling
<hw>Pul"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Whimpering; whining;
childish.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pulingly</ent>⟦br⟧
